@startuml arch_b_component
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam ArrowColor #336699
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam rectangleBorderColor #336699

title Architecture B — N-Tier Layered Architecture\nComponent & Layer Diagram

actor "Student (Browser)" as S

rectangle "N-Tier Layered Architecture" {

  rectangle "Layer 1: Presentation Layer" #LightBlue {
    component [FastAPI Router\n/api/feeds/rss] as ROUTER
  }

  rectangle "Layer 2: Business Logic Layer" #LightYellow {
    component [AggregatorFacade\nfetch_all_opportunities()] as FACADE
    component [RSSAdapter\nFeedparser XML] as RSS
    component [AdzunaAdapter\nAdzuna REST API] as ADZ
    component [JoobleAdapter\nJooble REST API] as JOO
  }

  rectangle "Layer 3: Data Access Layer" #LightSalmon {
    component [SQLAlchemy ORM\nRepository] as ORM
  }

  rectangle "Layer 4: Data Storage Layer" #Wheat {
    database [PostgreSQL\nrss_items table] as DB
  }
}

cloud "External Services" #PaleGreen {
  [RSS Feeds\n(Internshala / HackerEarth\n/ DevPost XML)] as EXT_RSS
  [Adzuna REST API\n(JSON)] as EXT_ADZ
  [Jooble REST API\n(JSON)] as EXT_JOO
}

S --> ROUTER : HTTP GET\n(synchronous)
ROUTER --> FACADE : fetch_all_opportunities()
FACADE --> RSS
FACADE --> ADZ
FACADE --> JOO
RSS --> EXT_RSS : HTTP GET (blocking ~1000ms)
ADZ --> EXT_ADZ : HTTP GET (blocking ~400ms)
JOO --> EXT_JOO : HTTP GET (blocking ~500ms)
FACADE --> ORM : insert_all()+select()
ORM --> DB : SQL INSERT + SELECT
DB --> ORM : rows
ORM --> FACADE : List[NormalizedRssItem]
FACADE --> ROUTER : merged result
ROUTER --> S : HTTP 200 JSON\n(~1500–2600ms total)

note bottom of FACADE
  All adapter calls are SEQUENTIAL
  and BLOCKING within a single
  HTTP request lifecycle.
  Total latency = sum of all external
  API response times.
end note

@enduml
